                    <locus target="#174v" facs="179">Fol. 174v</locus>
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                      Mentions a secondary owner, <q>This Dawit belongs to Gäbrä Märqorewos. A curse is proclaimed “on anyone who erases or steals, [may] his eyes [be gouged out] with a spear, his hands [cut off] with a knife.”</q></desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
